<h3>演示如何访问 TH 元素</h3>

<table>
 <tr>
   <th id="myTh">名字</th>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td>乔布斯</td>
 </tr>
</table>

<p>点击按钮来改变 TH 元素的文本。</p>

<button onclick="myFunction()">亲自试一试</button>

<p id="demo"></p>

<script>
function myFunction()
{
var x = document.getElementById("myTh");
x.innerHTML = "新的表头";
}
</script>

